get_D(C_Li: float | numpy.ndarray, T: float) → float | numpy.ndarray[source]#

Calculate the lithium ion diffusivity in the electrolyte solution at concentration C_Li and temperature T.

Parameters:

  • C_Li (float | 1D array) – Lithium ion concentration in the electrolyte [kmol/m^3].

  • T (float) – Battery temperature [K].

Returns:

D (float | 1D array) – Lithium ion diffusivity in the electrolyte [m^2/s].
